h2. Installation

<img class="left_img" src="{resource: reuth}" alt="A bride near Reuth."/>
**Installation consists of just three easy steps**:

# Create a directory for KTTGS.
# Copy the two current zip files to this directory.
# Unzip both files there.

I use the following script to unpackage the version and to create a basic
HTML from the provided skeleton (for further information concerning the 
installation process please check the READ.ME file).
<pre><code>
mkdir kttgs_installation
cp BikeTourXml-0.5.zip ./kttgs_installation
cp BikeTourXml-0.5-libs.zip ./kttgs_installation
cd ./kttgs_installation
unzip BikeTourXml-0.5.zip
unzip BikeTourXml-0.5-libs.zip 
</code></pre>

And the installation is done. Let's create our first tour.
<pre><code>
/home/tom/bin/apache-ant-1.6.2/bin/ant gen-skeleton
/home/tom/bin/apache-ant-1.6.2/bin/ant gen-tour-html
</code></pre>


